{"tid":667193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★IT男通宵工作右耳失聰　醫生：長期戴耳機損聽力","createTime":"2018-05-16T13:55:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T08:16:14.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dd646bf8118ea0a4b2a5ba6a1e37328f7fc7a165","tid":667193,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T13:55:44.000Z","msg":"福建福州23歲的邵先生從事手機遊戲開發工作，常常要捱夜。邵先生在近日的一個通宵後，驚見右耳失去聽力，經醫生檢查後確診為突發性耳聾，目前正接受治療。醫生表示，突發性耳聾常見於工作壓力太大，且沒有足夠休息。此外，長期配戴耳機，尤其是入耳式耳機，亦很容易會損傷聽力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180514/bkncn-20180514001021821-0514_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180514%2Fbkncn-20180514001021821-0514_05011_001.html&d=8jmk2lYNBG50uK1ZiHh80mi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=8bc179d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180514/bkncn-20180514001021821-0514_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ceb13ba358331a604b568a713e38bc84c6a8b1ad","tid":667193,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T13:55:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db52a96af44a25bc31396649a9e703b607cb989e","tid":667193,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:10:30.000Z","msg":"我隻耳仔都就報廢了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf9da306e6abd173561a921b539d2ff72b2c6e0c","tid":667193,"uid":178110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T05:07:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3f5b399ee914e38ccee25f91dd10bbfae4ae8c58","tid":667193,"uid":19454,"like":0,